snippet.textDisplay:
"The time your game is most vulnerable is when you're ahead; never let up" - Rod laver

If you watched the match live, this quote was displayed on court somewhere in the fourth set when fed still looked like he was done. McEnroe commented on how the quote applies to sandgren and I was like nah this match is over.

The next time I'm on court and feel like there's no way out, i hope i remember this.
